 is the same as attribute 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_clinical_terminology_code">CLINICAL TERMINOLOGY CODE</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_aids_defining_illness_code_adult__snomed_ct_">AIDS DEFINING ILLNESS CODE ADULT (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_information/clinical_coding/snomed_ct.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">SNOMED_CT</xref>
® concept ID which is used to identify the type of Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome (AIDS) defining illness a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 is diagnosed with.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_aids_defining_illness_code_adult__snomed_ct_">AIDS DEFINING ILLNESS CODE ADULT (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is used for adult 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSONS</xref>
 over 15 years of age.  </p>
